snippet.title: Offensive Combat: Redux! - OFFICIAL LAUNCH TRAILER
snippet.description: Offensive Combat: Redux! (http://bit.ly/OCRedux) is a fast-paced, irreverent online FPS game based in the Offensive Combat universe. OC:R lets you show your skill and play as a number of different characters including Commandos, Aliens, Geckos, Chickens, Orcs, Pirates and meme-inspired skins, as you match-up against up to 15 other players on each map. With 6 maps at launch and multiple modes including Deathmatch, Team Deathmatch, Capture Point Exploration and Bot Mode, and more content in the works, Offensive Combat: Redux! is the next major FPS game that you won't want to miss.
